{"tid":1078824,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[三國冷知識] 原來曹操係人妻控","createTime":"2019-03-26T13:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T12:56:57.000Z","uid":191650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d004bb24d8a0334131c0f6c993454a1b3f967192","tid":1078824,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"歷史上，曹操一共娶了15房妻妾，其中的「人妻」着實不少。比如說，何進的兒媳婦尹夫人，秦宜祿的妻子杜夫人，袁熙的老婆甄姬，還有張濟的妻子等。這些在《三國志&middot;張繡傳》、《三國志&middot;關羽傳》以及《三國志&middot;何冒傳》中都有記載。<br />\n<br />\n關於曹操究竟為何喜歡人妻的說法也有好幾種。第一種說法是曹操想通過娶別人的妻子，達到政治聯姻的目的，增強自己的權勢，鞏固政權。還有一種說法是曹操為了滿足個人的生理需求，喜歡人妻純粹是個人癖好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzTyuWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzTyuWy.jpg&h=335b6e4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"347d54992fc303be9df090c3a06186ea299b9a22","tid":1078824,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:44:09.000Z","msg":"大小二喬"},{"pid":"31bd4154b52c41f0ddf0db8398057f9f145f2d31","tid":1078824,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"甄氏係曹丕皇后喎"},{"pid":"672b8b824e6c40e434077349157f549b5bbabc91","tid":1078824,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31bd4154b52c41f0ddf0db8398057f9f145f2d31","tid":1078824,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"甄氏係曹丕皇后喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"曹丕皇后係郭女王"},{"pid":"49f5b7a2ea0a304c0fd65608ab9ae8a4da8bcd72","tid":1078824,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"甄姬<img sr